title: 3 Tracks with the Modbap Trinity Drum Synth
description:
Modbap Trinity is a 3 channel digital drum and percussion voice for Eurorack or MIDI. Let's check it out and make some music.

Get a Trinity
At Patchwerks: https://shrsl.com/3u6f5
At Perfect Circuit: http://bit.ly/3uF9Lsi
